<SYNC Start=1656725><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1656801><P Class=KRCC>
모두들 그렇게 말해
<SYNC Start=1658301><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1658302><P Class=KRCC>
